// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0394 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: ee443a45-85e0-56d3-b418-2a9e33a97618

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
